'''Sara Corner''' is an Indian [[beauty pageant]] contestant who won [[Miss India World]] in 2001 and represented India at [[Miss World 2001]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Beauty for all seasons|url=http://www.thehindu.com/thehindu/lf/2002/06/20/stories/2002062002860200.htm|accessdate=7 February 2015|work=[[The Hindu]]|date=20 June 2002}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Celina Jaitly|url=http://www.timescontent.com/syndication-photos/reprint/fashion/264833/celina-jaitly-sara-corner-maheshwar.html|accessdate=7 February 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Sara Corner|url=http://www.seasonsindia.com/modelwatch/sara_sea.htm|accessdate=7 February 2015}}</ref> Corner was born in Kolkata in an [[Anglo-Indian]] family. She is graduated in [[Bachelor in Economics]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Sara Corner – 2001|url=http://www.mensxp.com/entertainment/gossip/8892-25-hottest-miss-india-worlds-you-should-know-p13.html|website=[[MensXP.com]]|accessdate=7 February 2015}}</ref>
